|--------------------------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------------|-----------|------------------------------------------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------|---------------|--------------------------------------------|
| Re-entrancy in `finalizeRescueFailedDeposits`    | Implement a re-entrancy guard or ensure state updates are performed beforehand | High 🔥   | Attacker, Contract administrators        | An attacker can exploit potential re-entrancy in the rescue logic           | Vulnerability | `finalizeRescueFailedDeposits` function    |
